This project is a Python-based sports analytics tool that identifies potential NBA breakout players by comparing statistical performance across the current and previous season. Player statistics are retrieved from Basketball-Reference using Python, processed with Pandas, and analyzed to identify breakout players based on year-over-year performance improvements.


 !Visuals](https://github.com/akareese/NBA-Breakout-Season-Analysis-/blob/bd6f2dc7d9c7214b79c7663db3adf1e6fb151aca/demo.jpg).

